{"tid":2157680,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《回魂夜》Leon + 阿群 搪膠公仔套裝","createTime":"2020-08-15T07:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T15:20:29.000Z","uid":41343,"like":7,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"be7724846c8b0b5d9e7fd2ae2c53a0eb52384922","tid":2157680,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:46:17.000Z","msg":"今年8月將會好猛呀！為慶祝《回魂夜》在香港上映25周年，PLAY x Unbox x Celestial Pictures 合作推出經典電影系列《回魂夜》搪膠公仔套裝！是次更找來香港設計師 JIM DREAMS 為公仔創作設計造型，務求為香港經典電影注入香港特有的手工味道呢！VINART SUPREME 回魂夜搪膠公仔套裝將於8月22日隆重上市！ <a href=\"http://www.playtoy.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.playtoy.com.hk&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8Qy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=ca64cd34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.playtoy.com.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n~VINART SUPREME 回魂夜搪膠公仔套裝小資料~<br />\n商品内容：Leon x 1、阿群x 1、捉鬼用具行李箱 x 1、練膽炮仗 x 1<br />\n商品素材：搪膠、PVC (部分小配件包含 PVC 素材)<br />\n商品高度：約6吋<br />\n商品定價 :  HKD 498 / 套<br />\n<br />\n*圖片只供參考，實際商品可能有異。<br />\n<br />\nThis year, Hong Kong Classic Movie &ldquo;Out Of The Dark&rdquo; comes to the 25th movie anniversary, in order to revive Hong Kong classic movie characters but also the collective memory of audience to the present, PLAY x Unbox x Celestial Pictures has invited Hong Kong designer, Jim Chan from JIM DREAMS and produced VINART SUPREME Out Of The Dark Vinyl Figurine Combo Set.  The whole package is here, from the backing card to a classic figure that would take you back to the movie. Own it on 22 Aug 2020 at our online shop or local physical stores.<br />\n<br />\n#hongkong #hongkongclassicmovie #outofthedark #celestialpictures #playtoyhongkong #unboxindustries #jimdreams #comingsoon #vinyltoys #sofubi<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MWA0Rs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MWA0Rs.jpg&h=c9c767c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/playtoy.com.hk/photos/a.1632997113645758/2787324154879709/\" dat